des:
Listen to this story with a timeless lesson. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 
Hobbes was a corporate tsar, a vast empire of a micro economy hidden deep in the forest. In this story discover how he joins the Jedi force and finds the good in himself, from the characters of the Indian Folk Tale, Punyakoti. Good deeds bring you Punya, a Hindu Karmic Concept, With a high goodness index, you visit the Jedi Heaven of Light, with Yoda and other characters, a prelude to the Trio, this story is a must addition to your bag of stories, share it and its timeless message.
